<h2 class="bold font-l">Episode 2 Unseen Intruder</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In &quot;Final Fantasy XIII-2,&quot; an on-screen title blended with the landscape informs players that this is &quot;Episode 2 Unseen Intruder&quot; as Serah Farron's sister Lightning narrates. </p>
